text: The most popular theme from my favorite game in the series after TTT2. Do we have any news concerning Tekken X Street Fighter? text: With Tekken 7 being announced, Harada did say they're still working on TxSF. They're still putting down the basics for it, and they're still working out how to get past Street Fighter's jumpy/floaty gameplay, since Tekken's jumping physics and attacks work completely differently. The main issue is adapting SF's gameplay. Beyond that, nothing else. Least it's not cancelled though.
